THIRD-PARTY DEPENDENCIES

This project includes software developed by third parties. See the
individual Cargo.toml files for a complete list of dependencies and
their respective licenses.

Key dependencies include:
- jsonwebtoken (MIT) - JWT validation
- p256 (Apache-2.0 OR MIT) - Elliptic curve cryptography
- tokio (MIT) - Async runtime
- serde (Apache-2.0 OR MIT) - Serialization
- reqwest (Apache-2.0 OR MIT) - HTTP client
